SUMMARY:Pride Parade & Festival
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by the City of Tigard in partnership with TTSD. Parade s
 tarts at 2pm at 113th Ave & Durham\, continuing down Durham eastbound and 
 ending at Tigard High School. View the parade anywhere on Durham. Festival
  inside Tigard HS after the parade with multiple vendors and activities.\n
LOCATION:Starts at 113th Ave. and Durham Rd and ends at Tigard High School
URL:https://www.tigard-or.gov/explore-tigard/community-events/pride-festiva
 l
END:VEVENT
